Feature: Delete Interest
  As a user
  I want to remove an interest
  So that I can withdraw from a proposal

  Scenario: Successfully delete an interest
    Given There is an existing interest with id "1"
    When I delete the interest with id "1"
    Then The response code is 204
    And The interest no longer exists

  Scenario: Delete an interest that does not exist
    When I delete the interest with id "999"
    Then The response code is 404
    And The error message is "Interest not found"
